Overview
Wiens is a family owned and operated furniture, appliance, and mattress retail store located 20 minutes South of Winnipeg, in the thriving town of Niverville. The Wiens family started their humble operations in 1939 as a harness and shoe repair shop. They have evolved over the years, and four generations later, are now a leader in the furniture, appliance, and mattress retail market for Winnipeg and Southern Manitoba. Our store showcases 20,000 sq ft of retail space, with 5,000 sq ft of that being a brand-new state-of-the art appliance showroom. With this new expansion we have been able to establish ourselves as leaders in the high-end appliance market with brands such as Jenn-Air, Thermador, Bosch, Monogram, Sub-zero and Wolf. We aim to be the go-to furniture, appliance, and mattress retailer for Winnipeg and Southern Manitoba based on selection, quality, and exceptional customer service.
To see a tour of our store please visit our YouTube page at www.youtube.com/watch?v=tqY_y8qvpPY
Responsibilities
Customer service, provide a personalized shopping experience to all clientele
Manage the full sales process for furniture, appliances, and mattresses
Develop and maintain strong knowledge of all products
Maintain showroom floor appearance to the Wiens standard
Success Factors
Strong communication skills and interpersonal skills
Strong character and inviting personality
Focus on the customer experience
Working knowledge of MS Office and ability to learn new computer programs
Strong analytical skills and problem-solving skills
Ability to work well independently and with others
Ability to process work efficiently and accurately
Dependable, self-motivated, and results driven
Ability to stand for periods of time
Scheduling flexibility, must be able to work Monday to Saturday days, with some evenings
Qualifications
Sales experience in a retail environment would be an asset, but not required
Compensation
Compensation is comprised of a base salary, commission, and bonus
Reasonable expectations for earnings would be between $60,000 and $100,000, but could be higher
To learn more about Wiens Furniture please visit our website at www.wiensfurniture.ca or follow us on Instagram, Facebook, YouTube, and LinkedIn.
Wiens recognizes that in order to provide the exceptional customer service that we’re known for, we must hire Sales Associates that share our passion and vision. If this sounds like it could be a fit for you we look forward to hearing from you.
Job Types: Full-time, Permanent
Salary: $60,000.00-$100,000.00 per year
